# Configure customer-managed keys with Azure Key Vault for Applied AI Services

The process to enable Customer-Managed Keys with Azure Key Vault for Applied AI Services varies by product. Use these links for service-specific instructions:

* [Cognitive Search encryption of data at rest](https://docs.microsoft.com/azure/search/search-security-manage-encryption-keys)

* [Form Recognizer encryption of data at rest](https://docs.microsoft.com/azure/cognitive-services/form-recognizer/encrypt-data-at-rest)

* [Metrics Advisor encryption of data at rest](https://docs.microsoft.com/azure/cognitive-services/metrics-advisor/encryption#customer-managed-keys-with-azure-key-vault)

* [Video Analyzer encryption of data at rest](https://docs.microsoft.com/azure/azure-video-analyzer/video-analyzer-docs/customer-managed-keys)


